      "description": "Well-kept, good-condition example that presents nicely and has clearly been cared for. It\u2019s clean inside and out with a strong overall look, and it offers a lot to like for someone wanting a solid, enjoyable car without paying mint-condition money. Not perfect, of course, with the normal signs of use and age you\u2019d expect, but still a very appealing, honest car.",
