      "description": "Fair-condition vehicle that shows normal age and regular use, but remains a decent, usable driver. Expect visible cosmetic wear inside and out, including paint blemishes, worn interior surfaces, and general signs of everyday use. It presents respectably overall, but it is not a showroom example and should be approached as a practical vehicle rather than a perfect one. A solid option for someone looking for dependable transportation at a more affordable price point.",
