      "description": "A budget-friendly opportunity for the right buyer, this vehicle offers straightforward value and dependable basics at an accessible price point. It shows its age cosmetically, but it remains a practical choice for everyday transportation, a first car, or a project for someone who appreciates a solid deal. If you\u2019re looking for inexpensive mobility without the premium price tag, this is a smart option worth a closer look.",
