    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and offers a great opportunity for someone who wants a cheap daily, a backup vehicle, or a weekend project. It\u2019s being priced with its condition in mind, and I\u2019d rather be upfront and fair than dress it up as something it\u2019s not. If you want honest value and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, this could be a smart buy.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
