      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project or daily beater with a strong-running engine, responsive automatic transmission, and a chassis that still feels planted on the road. Not cosmetically perfect and shows its age, but it starts, moves out well, and has plenty of usable life for someone who wants dependable basic transportation or a platform to sort and improve. Great value for a hands-on owner looking for affordable wheels with good mechanical upside.",
