      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough for the right buyer, this car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that turns errands into a little adventure. It carries a gritty, lived-in presence and offers a great opportunity for someone who wants affordable wheels with personality, a project with promise, or a practical runabout that still has stories left to tell. If you appreciate value, potential, and a vehicle with unmistakable character, this one is easy to imagine making your own.",
